			<p>
				<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">As a RE project developer, SECI has installed 122.7 MW of RE projects and 1325 MW of projects are in pipeline. Through its own projects, SECI has supplied 72 MU of RE in FY 2023-24. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

